            title="Privacy Policy"
            content="At OnBoard, we are committed to protecting your privacy. We do not collect any personal information, and we do not use cookies or any other tracking technologies. Your visit to our site is anonymous, and we do not gather or store any data related to your browsing activity. We respect your privacy and strive to maintain a secure and transparent online environment for all our visitors. If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please feel free to contact us."
          />
